<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Get Started - AI Guilt</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/vue@3.2.36/dist/vue.global.js"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #000000;
            color: #ffffff;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .navbar {
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
        }
        .navbar-brand, .nav-link {
            color: #ffffff !important;
        }
        .hero-section {
            padding: 80px 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #000000 100%);
            border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
        }
        .feature-card {
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #333;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }
        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #007bff;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .join-form {
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #333;
        }
        .form-control {
            background-color: #252525;
            border: 1px solid #333;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 12px;
        }
        .form-control:focus {
            background-color: #2a2a2a;
            color: #ffffff;
            border-color: #007bff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.2rem rgba(0,123,255,0.25);
        }
        .btn-join {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #007bff, #00bfff);
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .btn-join:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,123,255,0.3);
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .feed-post {
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border: 1px solid #333;
        }
        .post-content {
            color: #ddd;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        .post-meta {
            color: #888;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .post-author {
            color: #007bff;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .post-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .action-button {
            background: none;
            border: none;
            color: #888;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 5px;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .action-button:hover {
            color: #007bff;
        }
        .alert {
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .alert-success {
            background-color: rgba(25, 135, 84, 0.2);
            border: 1px solid #198754;
            color: #75b798;
        }
        .alert-danger {
            background-color: rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.2);
            border: 1px solid #dc3545;
            color: #ea868f;
        }
        .form-loading {
            opacity: 0.7;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .spinner-border {
            width: 1rem;
            height: 1rem;
            margin-right: 0.5rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="app">
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg">
            <div class="container">
                <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">AI Guilt</a>
                <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
                    <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                </button>
                <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                    <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="/">Home</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="/about.html">About</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="/login.php">Login</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>

        <section class="hero-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row align-items-center">
                    <div class="col-lg-6">
                        <h2 class="mb-4">AI Guilt Feed</h2>
                        <div v-for="post in posts" :key="post.id" class="feed-post">
                            <p class="post-content">{{ post.content }}</p>
                            <div class="post-meta">
                                <span class="post-author">{{ post.author }}</span>
                                <span>{{ post.timestamp }}</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="post-actions">
                                <button class="action-button">
                                    <i class="fas fa-heart"></i>
                                    <span>{{ post.likes }} Likes</span>
                                </button>
                                <button class="action-button">
                                    <i class="fas fa-comment"></i>
                                    <span>{{ post.comments }} Comments</span>
                                </button>
                                <button class="action-button">
                                    <i class="fas fa-share"></i>
                                    <span>Share</span>
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-6">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-6" v-for="feature in features" :key="feature.title">
                                <div class="feature-card">
                                    <div class="feature-icon">{{ feature.icon }}</div>
                                    <h3>{{ feature.title }}</h3>
                                    <p>{{ feature.description }}</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="container my-5">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="join-form" id="joinForm" :class="{ 'form-loading': loading }">
                        <h2 class="mb-4">Create Your Account</h2>
                        <div v-if="alert" :class="['alert', `alert-${alert.type}`]">
                            {{ alert.message }}
                        </div>
                        <form @submit.prevent="handleSubmit">
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label for="username" class="form-label">Username</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="username" 
                                       v-model="form.username" required 
                                       :class="{ 'is-invalid': errors.username }"
                                       minlength="3">
                                <div class="invalid-feedback" v-if="errors.username">
                                    {{ errors.username }}
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label for="email" class="form-label">Email</label>
                                <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" 
                                       v-model="form.email" required
                                       :class="{ 'is-invalid': errors.email }">
                                <div class="invalid-feedback" v-if="errors.email">
                                    {{ errors.email }}
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label for="password" class="form-label">Password</label>
                                <input type="password" class="form-control" id="password" 
                                       v-model="form.password" required
                                       :class="{ 'is-invalid': errors.password }"
                                       minlength="6">
                                <div class="invalid-feedback" v-if="errors.password">
                                    {{ errors.password }}
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label for="confirmPassword" class="form-label">Confirm Password</label>
                                <input type="password" class="form-control" id="confirmPassword" 
                                       v-model="form.confirmPassword" required
                                       :class="{ 'is-invalid': errors.confirmPassword }">
                                <div class="invalid-feedback" v-if="errors.confirmPassword">
                                    {{ errors.confirmPassword }}
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-join" :disabled="loading">
                                <span v-if="loading" class="spinner-border" role="status">
                                    <span class="visually-hidden">Loading...</span>
                                </span>
                                {{ loading ? 'Creating Account...' : 'Create Account' }}
                            </button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <h1 class="display-4 mb-4">Join the AI Ethics Discussion</h1>
                    <p class="lead mb-4">Connect with others experiencing AI-related ethical concerns. Share experiences, find support, and contribute to meaningful discussions about the future of AI.</p>
                    <button class="btn btn-join btn-lg" @click="scrollToForm">Get Started Now</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="signup.js"></script>
    <script>
        const app = Vue.createApp({
            data() {
                return {
                    form: {
                        username: '',
                        email: '',
                        password: '',
                        confirmPassword: ''
                    },
                    loading: false,
                    alert: null,
                    errors: {
                        username: '',
                        email: '',
                        password: '',
                        confirmPassword: ''
                    },
                    features: [
                        {
                            icon: 'üí≠',
                            title: 'Share Experiences',
                            description: 'Connect with others facing similar AI ethical dilemmas and share your journey.'
                        },
                        {
                            icon: 'üéß',
                            title: 'Expert Insights',
                            description: 'Access exclusive podcasts featuring AI ethics experts and practitioners.'
                        },
                        {
                            icon: 'ü§ù',
                            title: 'Community Support',
                            description: 'Find support and guidance from our growing community of AI practitioners.'
                        },
                        {
                            icon: 'üìö',
                            title: 'Resource Library',
                            description: 'Access curated resources on AI ethics, guidelines, and best practices.'
                        }
                    ],
                    posts: [
                        {
                            id: 1,
                            content: "Just implemented an AI system that helps detect early signs of mental health issues. Struggling with the ethical implications of predictive healthcare. Anyone else facing similar challenges? #AIEthics #Healthcare",
                            author: "Dr. Sarah Chen",
                            timestamp: "2 hours ago",
                            likes: 45,
                            comments: 12
                        },
                        {
                            id: 2,
                            content: "Working on an AI art generator and feeling conflicted about the impact on human artists. How do we balance innovation with protecting creative livelihoods? Looking for perspectives from both tech and art communities.",
                            author: "Marcus Rodriguez",
                            timestamp: "5 hours ago",
                            likes: 89,
                            comments: 34
                        },
                        {
                            id: 3,
                            content: "Today's dilemma: Our AI recruitment tool shows bias against certain demographics despite our best efforts to eliminate it. How are others handling similar situations? Need advice on maintaining fairness while leveraging AI capabilities.",
                            author: "Lisa Thompson",
                            timestamp: "1 day ago",
                            likes: 156,
                            comments: 67
                        }
                    ]
                }
            },
            methods: {
                async handleSubmit() {
                    // Reset previous errors and alerts
                    this.errors = {
                        username: '',
                        email: '',
                        password: '',
                        confirmPassword: ''
                    };
                    this.alert = null;
                    this.loading = true;

                    try {
                        const response = await handleSignup(this.form);
                        this.alert = {
                            type: 'success',
                            message: response.message
                        };
                        // Clear form after successful signup
                        this.form = {
                            username: '',
                            email: '',
                            password: '',
                            confirmPassword: ''
                        };
                    } catch (error) {
                        this.alert = {
                            type: 'danger',
                            message: error.message
                        };
                    } finally {
                        this.loading = false;
                    }
                },
                scrollToForm() {
                    document.getElementById('joinForm').scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth' });
                }
            }
        }).mount('#app');
    </script>
</body>
</html>
